---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Solutions | SGA Industrial Automations"
  description="Explore automation, IIoT, control panel and energy management solutions from SGA Industrial Automations."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <h1>Solutions</h1>
    <p>Industrial automation & IIoT built around your machines, lines and plants.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="solutions-grid">
    <article class="sol-card" id="industrial-automation">
      <h2>Machine & Line Automation</h2>
      <p>
        PLC, HMI, servo and VFD based automation for discrete machines, process lines and utilities —
        engineered for stability, safety and maintainability.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>PLC, HMI & SCADA programming</li>
        <li>Retrofits for old relay / hard-wired systems</li>
        <li>Interlocks, safety logic & alarms</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="sol-card" id="iiot">
      <h2>IIoT & Remote Monitoring</h2>
      <p>
        Connect your machines and panels securely to the cloud and monitor OEE, downtime, energy and
        production KPIs in real-time.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Data collection from PLCs, meters & drives</li>
        <li>Dashboards for OEE, downtime and availability</li>
        <li>Email / SMS / WhatsApp alerts and reports</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="sol-card" id="panels">
      <h2>Control Panel Design & Manufacturing</h2>
      <p>
        MCC, PCC, PLC, VFD, marshalling and control desks — designed, wired and tested to meet industrial
        standards and plant requirements.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>GA drawings & detailed schematics</li>
        <li>Neat wiring, ferruling & tagging</li>
        <li>Factory testing & on-site integration</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="sol-card" id="energy-management">
      <h2>Energy & Utility Management</h2>
      <p>
        Monitor and optimize power, compressed air, water and other utilities to reduce wastage and cost.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Energy meters & multi-circuit logging</li>
        <li>Utility dashboards for kWh, kVA, PF & more</li>
        <li>Threshold-based alerts for abnormal usage</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Need a custom automation or IIoT solution?</h2>
    <p>Share your machine, process or panel requirement. We’ll propose a practical, implementation-ready approach.</p>
    <div class="cta-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact">Talk to Us</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:+917673902729">Call: +91 76739 02729</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .page-header p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #9ca3af;
  }

  .solutions-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .sol-card {
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.9);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .sol-card h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .sol-card p {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    color: #d1d5db;
  }

  .sol-card ul {
    margin: 0 0 0 1.1rem;
    padding: 0;
    color: #9ca3af;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.5);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 42px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1.3rem;
    color: #d1d5db;
  }

  .cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.45rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.6rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform 0.12s ease, box-shadow 0.12s ease, background 0.15s,
      border-color 0.15s, color 0.15s;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: radial-gradient(
      circle at top left,
      #22d3ee,
      #0ea5e9 40%,
      #4f46e5 100%
    );
    color: #020617;
    box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.6);
    border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.9);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.9);
  }

  .btn-ghost {
    background: transparent;
    color: #e5e7eb;
    border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.8);
  }

  .btn-ghost:hover {
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
    border-color: #22d3ee;
    box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.4);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .solutions-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
